{Speech 7}{}{My first time.\nI was never particularly shy, but when the time came for my first time, I felt for the first time as if the whole world was watching me. In part I was right - Cthulha, Tabak, Sintez, FORevenge, Killermike and the other gang members were sizing me up - they had become my whole world over the past few weeks. Some watched with interest, some chuckled quietly in the corner.\n- Get on with it already! What are you staring at her for? - bellowed Sintez, - Want us to light some candles for you?\nA booming laugh rolled through the room, swelling into a hollow echo.\n- Stick a candle in... - Issa started to say, but Killermike shut him up at once with a smack to the back of the head. Issa flew across the room from the slap of a heavy Advanced Power Armor gauntlet and flopped down like a sack of manure, which turned the laughter in the room into frenzied howling. I couldn't help smiling too.\n- You shouldn't be smiling, you should be starting what we all gathered here for - Cthulha said calmly, making everyone fall silent.\nI knew this moment would come sooner or later, but I never managed to prepare for it. And how could you prepare for such a thing - not everyone is capable of freely fucking under several dozen pairs of eyes.\nBut I knew that how the gang members would look at me depended on this, perhaps even my survival was at stake.\nI loosened my belt and dropped my pants, pulling out my already considerably enlarged cock. With one lightning-quick movement, as Cthulha had taught, I shoved it into her ass. In response she lurched forward, trying to run. I gripped her ass hard with my hands and began to fuck her, at first slowly, then faster and harder. She kept trying to break free of my hands, which even started to amuse me. I could already feel that I would soon come inside her. At that moment Vut came up to me and pressed a gauss pistol into my hands with the words "you know what to do."\nI aimed the pistol's muzzle at her head and, just as I was about to come, pulled the trigger. Her head fell off and rolled across the floor, and from the neck arteries, as if from a hose, blood began to gush. I kept coming inside her to the steady mooing of the second head. When I finished, I shot off her second head too. That's how I fucked a brahmin for the first time.\nA minute later Mesh came up to me, put a hand on my shoulder and said: - Tomorrow we go fuck little girls in Klamath. Though I can see brahmins aren't bad for you either - we'll save you a couple.\nThe hall filled with wild laughter again. This time I laughed along with everyone, calmly now. Now I'm a real Zerg.\nChuvachello.}
