{Speech 9}{}{Be-Be's Diary\nEntry from 22.04.\nThe day boded nothing good, all my screwed-in-the-head comrades-in-arms were resting on their bunks after a session of pounding brahmins. \nI couldn't sleep so I went out into the wasteland to fill my flask with fresh human blood, so I wouldn't suffer from thirst during the drawn-out genocide operation in Klamath. \nMy feet carried me to BrokenHills, on arrival I found no one there, which couldn't help but disappoint me.\nI decided to wait a little and suddenly a stunning bitch walks into town.  So I sidle up to her and say: Hey, dammit, let me have you, or I'll give you a club right between the eyes. Naturally she pissed herself hot and the bitch was already spreading her legs. But me, dammit, I'm not like that - I can't do it without foreplay. So in short I tell her: "Now QUICK, bitch, dance for me and at the same time spell out my name in flowers on the ground"\nThis diary's worn me out somehow. In short: I fucked her in every hole, and then I also smashed up some Serb who for some reason doesn't like ramming brahmins in the ass and so wages war against me.\nThis diary must absolutely be read to children, let them know from a young age what is good and what is bad. \nBe-Be}
