{Speech 14}{}{This story happened long ago, when I, DJ Rabbit, was the mayor of Klamath. Yes, yes, in those harsh times Nikko was already in his grave, the Patriarch had not yet crawled out of his drinking binge, and justice was dealt by me, sometimes I even wanted to call myself Sir Rabbitmon. It was a summer evening, the air smelled deliciously of decomposing corpses that had piled up on the approaches to town. I stood by the well, savoring the silence. Beside me Cthulha, squinting, watched the setting sun and finished off a Haitian cigar. Suddenly the wind carried to me someone's fierce argument. The few townsfolk fighting over something again? I took a dose of jet and went toward the sound. Reaching the alleys, I saw two whores heatedly screaming at each other. Without much thought, I fired into the air and inquired what the matter was. It turned out both these whores live in the same house, and both have a one-year-old child. During the day, while one of them honestly serviced the zergs, the other killed her own baby and slipped it to the first, taking her child. They tried to expose each other before me, and I just couldn't understand what was wrong with such a fair exchange. In the end I demanded that the surviving child be brought, and said that if they didn't stop cackling, I would cut it in half. One immediately began wailing that the child must live, and I put a bullet in her forehead. The second said she didn't care, and I put a bullet in her forehead. Then I put a bullet in the child's forehead. Then I took another dose and went to admire the sunset. \nDJKrolik. Sir Rabbit.}
