{Speech 15}{}{Early morning. Fog. Insects chirp away in the bushes. The mining town of Redding wakes up. The sheriff heads to his dusty office, the miners of the "Morning Star," living up to the name, trudge off to the pits. A dog ran past, the casino doors opened. The time has come to destroy their little world. I pull out my baby - a Rockwell bazooka, load it and plant a rocket right into the sheriff's building. I reload, another shot - and the bar's roof comes down on the morning patrons. I take a vindicator and head down, toward the battle. Two guards with rifles are already aiming at me, but how are they going to pierce power armor? Bullets ring as they bounce off, and I walk right up to one of them point-blank and pull the trigger. The second guard, splattered with his friend's guts, immediately turns and runs, but a plasma grenade catches up with him, and now my favorite part begins. I walk along Redding's main street and toss grenades through the windows, and with an alien blaster I turn the little people running out into ash. Five people, ten, thirty - it all blurred together in a bloody frenzy. I pull out my long cock and start masturbating. People die under the ruins of their own homes, suffocating on carbon monoxide - and I stand in the middle of town and jerk off. At last, orgasm is near, and my tool needs a sacrifice. Just the thing - a nurse from the garden church, dragging some old man. I come up from behind and relieve her of her burden, then tear off the girl's head, which, a frozen expression of horror on its face, flies off into a ditch. I dip my cock into her warm windpipe and come, savoring the streams of blood from her arteries. Now this town too has learned what the words "Sintez wrecks everyone" really mean.\nsintez}
